<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <img src="./awokien-pfp.png" alt="Awokien profile picture">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <meta
        name="viewport"
        content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
    >

    <meta
        name="description"
        content="Awokien is a Roblox developer and Luau programmer contributing to experiences with over 100 million combined visits."
    >

    <title>Awokien | Roblox Developer</title>

    <link
        rel="preconnect"
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"
    >

    <link
        rel="preconnect"
        href="https://fonts.gstatic.com"
        crossorigin
    >

    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet"
    >

    <style>
        :root {
            --background: #050713;
            --background-secondary: #090d1d;
            --card: rgba(15, 21, 43, 0.72);
            --card-hover: rgba(22, 31, 61, 0.9);
            --border: rgba(132, 168, 255, 0.16);
            --text: #f7f9ff;
            --muted: #a9b3cf;
            --blue: #4d8dff;
            --blue-light: #73b4ff;
            --purple: #985cff;
            --cyan: #46d9ff;
            --success: #63ffbd;
            --shadow: 0 25px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background:
                radial-gradient(
                    circle at 10% 20%,
                    rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.18),
                    transparent 35%
                ),
                radial-gradient(
                    circle at 90% 15%,
                    rgba(152, 92, 255, 0.15),
                    transparent 32%
                ),
                radial-gradient(
                    circle at 50% 95%,
                    rgba(70, 217, 255, 0.1),
                    transparent 35%
                ),
                var(--background);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
        }

        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: -2;
            opacity: 0.28;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025) 1px,
                    transparent 1px
                ),
                linear-gradient(
                    90deg,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025) 1px,
                    transparent 1px
                );
            background-size: 55px 55px;
            mask-image: linear-gradient(
                to bottom,
                black,
                transparent 90%
            );
        }

        body::after {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            top: -180px;
            right: -170px;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.2);
            filter: blur(120px);
            animation: floatGlow 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        button {
            font: inherit;
        }

        .container {
            width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 18px;
            left: 50%;
            z-index: 1000;
            width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(6, 9, 22, 0.72);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32);
            backdrop-filter: blur(22px);
        }

        .nav-inner {
            min-height: 70px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 25px;
            padding: 0 22px;
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 11px;
            font-size: 19px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .brand-logo {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(
                135deg,
                var(--blue),
                var(--purple)
            );
            box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.45);
        }

        .brand-logo::before {
            content: "A";
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 7px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border-radius: 11px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.25s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            color: white;
        }

        .nav-status {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 9px 13px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(99, 255, 189, 0.18);
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(99, 255, 189, 0.06);
            color: #adffdc;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--success);
            box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--success);
            animation: pulse 1.7s infinite;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 145px 0 85px;
        }

        .hero-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 70px;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            width: fit-content;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 9px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            padding: 9px 14px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(115, 180, 255, 0.22);
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.07);
            color: #b9d6ff;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .eyebrow-icon {
            color: var(--cyan);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            max-width: 760px;
            font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 92px);
            line-height: 0.96;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(
                90deg,
                var(--blue-light),
                var(--cyan),
                var(--purple)
            );
            background-size: 200% auto;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            animation: gradientMove 5s linear infinite;
        }

        .hero-description {
            max-width: 680px;
            margin-top: 28px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 20px);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .typed-line {
            min-height: 30px;
            margin-top: 19px;
            color: #dce9ff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .typed-text {
            color: var(--blue-light);
        }

        .cursor {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 2px;
            height: 18px;
            margin-left: 4px;
            transform: translateY(3px);
            background: var(--cyan);
            animation: blink 0.8s infinite;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 13px;
            margin-top: 34px;
        }

        .button {
            min-height: 52px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 9px;
            padding: 0 21px;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 800;
            transition:
                transform 0.25s ease,
                box-shadow 0.25s ease,
                background 0.25s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .button-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(
                135deg,
                var(--blue),
                var(--purple)
            );
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.27);
        }

        .button-primary:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .button-secondary {
            border-color: var(--border);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            color: #dfe6f8;
        }

        .button-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        .hero-card-wrap {
            position: relative;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
        }

        .hero-card-wrap::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 310px;
            height: 310px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(
                135deg,
                rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.6),
                rgba(152, 92, 255, 0.45)
            );
            filter: blur(85px);
            opacity: 0.55;
        }

        .profile-card {
            position: relative;
            width: min(100%, 410px);
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 26px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(122, 160, 255, 0.25);
            border-radius: 28px;
            background:
                linear-gradient(
                    145deg,
                    rgba(18, 26, 53, 0.92),
                    rgba(8, 12, 27, 0.86)
                );
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            animation: cardFloat 5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .profile-card::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 220px;
            height: 220px;
            top: -110px;
            right: -90px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(70, 217, 255, 0.14);
            filter: blur(18px);
        }

        .profile-top {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 92px;
            height: 92px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 3px solid rgba(115, 180, 255, 0.7);
            border-radius: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(
                135deg,
                #1c2d5b,
                #28164d
            );
            box-shadow: 0 0 35px rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.25);
            font-size: 38px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .profile-name {
            font-size: 25px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .profile-handle {
            margin-top: 5px;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .verified {
            display: inline-grid;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            place-items: center;
            margin-left: 4px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--blue);
            font-size: 11px;
            vertical-align: 3px;
        }

        .profile-bio {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            margin-top: 24px;
            padding: 17px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 17px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .mini-stats {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 17px;
        }

        .mini-stat {
            padding: 15px 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .mini-stat strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .mini-stat span {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 5px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .profile-stack {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }

        .tag {
            padding: 8px 11px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(115, 180, 255, 0.16);
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.07);
            color: #cbe0ff;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .section-header {
            max-width: 720px;
            margin-bottom: 46px;
        }

        .section-label {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 58px);
            line-height: 1.05;
            letter-spacing: -2.5px;
        }

        .section-description {
            margin-top: 18px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .stat-card,
        .service-card,
        .project-card,
        .contact-card {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: var(--card);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            transition:
                transform 0.28s ease,
                border-color 0.28s ease,
                background 0.28s ease;
        }

        .stat-card:hover,
        .service-card:hover,
        .project-card:hover,
        .contact-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-7px);
            border-color: rgba(115, 180, 255, 0.38);
            background: var(--card-hover);
        }

        .stat-card {
            padding: 28px;
            border-radius: 22px;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 37px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
        }

        .stat-title {
            margin-top: 9px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .service-card {
            min-height: 255px;
            padding: 27px;
            border-radius: 23px;
        }

        .service-icon {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(115, 180, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(
                135deg,
                rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.18),
                rgba(152, 92, 255, 0.12)
            );
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            margin-top: 23px;
            font-size: 21px;
            letter-spacing: -0.6px;
        }

        .service-card p {
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        .projects-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .project-card {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 330px;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
        }

        .project-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 260px;
            height: 260px;
            right: -130px;
            bottom: -130px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.11);
            filter: blur(10px);
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .project-card:hover::before {
            transform: scale(1.35);
        }

        .project-number {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .project-card h3 {
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 55px;
            font-size: 29px;
            letter-spacing: -1.3px;
        }

        .project-card p {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin-top: 14px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        .project-tags {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 26px;
        }

        .skill-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr;
            gap: 35px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .skill-intro {
            position: sticky;
            top: 120px;
        }

        .skills-list {
            display: grid;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .skill-row {
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: var(--card);
        }

        .skill-row-top {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .skill-row-top span:last-child {
            color: var(--blue-light);
        }

        .skill-bar {
            height: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-top: 14px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        }

        .skill-fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: var(--level);
            border-radius: inherit;
            background: linear-gradient(
                90deg,
                var(--blue),
                var(--cyan),
                var(--purple)
            );
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.45);
            transform-origin: left;
            animation: loadBar 1.2s ease both;
        }

        .contact-box {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 55px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(115, 180, 255, 0.24);
            border-radius: 30px;
            background:
                linear-gradient(
                    135deg,
                    rgba(77, 141, 255, 0.13),
                    rgba(152, 92, 255, 0.09)
                ),
                rgba(9, 13, 30, 0.76);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-box::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 320px;
            height: 320px;
            top: -170px;
            left: -150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(70, 217, 255, 0.13);
            filter: blur(25px);
        }

        .contact-box h2 {
            position: relative;
            font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 65px);
            letter-spacing: -3px;
        }

        .contact-box p {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 18px auto 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .contact-actions {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 13px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 35px 0 45px;
            color: #78839f;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition:
                opacity 0.75s ease,
                transform 0.75s ease;
        }

        .reveal.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        @keyframes gradientMove {
            to {
                background-position: 200% center;
            }
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            50% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            50% {
                opacity: 0.45;
                transform: scale(0.8);
            }
        }

        @keyframes cardFloat {
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-12px) rotate(0.4deg);
            }
        }

        @keyframes floatGlow {
            to {
                transform: translate(-80px, 80px) scale(1.15);
            }
        }

        @keyframes loadBar {
            from {
                transform: scaleX(0);
            }

            to {
                transform: scaleX(1);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 940px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero-grid,
            .skill-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .hero-grid {
                gap: 60px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                letter-spacing: -3px;
            }

            .profile-card {
                max-width: 520px;
            }

            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }

            .services-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }

            .skill-intro {
                position: static;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 650px) {
            .container {
                width: min(100% - 25px, 1180px);
            }

            .nav {
                top: 10px;
            }

            .nav-inner {
                min-height: 62px;
                padding: 0 15px;
            }

            .nav-status {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero {
                padding-top: 120px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 53px;
                letter-spacing: -3.2px;
            }

            .hero-description {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .button {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .stats-grid,
            .services-grid,
            .projects-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .mini-stats {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .profile-top {
                align-items: flex-start;
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .section {
                padding: 75px 0;
            }

            .section-title {
                letter-spacing: -1.8px;
            }

            .contact-box {
                padding: 42px 20px;
            }

            .contact-box h2 {
                letter-spacing: -2px;
            }
        }

        @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            *,
            *::before,
            *::after {
                scroll-behavior: auto !important;
                animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
                animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
                transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="nav">
        <div class="nav-inner">
            <a class="brand" href="#home">
                <span class="brand-logo"></span>
                <span>Awokien</span>
            </a>

            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="#about">About</a>
                <a href="#services">Services</a>
                <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
                <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
                <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
            </div>

            <div class="nav-status">
                <span class="status-dot"></span>
                Building new projects
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section class="hero" id="home">
            <div class="container hero-grid">
                <div class="hero-content reveal">
                    <div class="eyebrow">
                        <span class="eyebrow-icon">✦</span>
                        Roblox Developer & Luau Programmer
                    </div>

                    <h1>
                        Building the future of
                        <span class="gradient-text">Roblox.</span>
                    </h1>

                    <p class="hero-description">
                        Hey, I'm <strong>Awokien</strong>, also known as
                        <strong>@aawokiengamess</strong>. I'm a
                        16-year-old developer creating polished systems,
                        interfaces, tools and experiences for Roblox.
                    </p>

                    <div class="typed-line">
                        I build
                        <span class="typed-text" id="typed-text"></span>
                        <span class="cursor"></span>
                    </div>

